---
title: "US19 — Workout reminders"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>NotificationsScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>UpdateNotificationPrefs
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>NotificationGateway (local notifications)
  A->>B: toggle "Daily reminder" on
  B->>C: setEnabled(daily_reminder, true)
  C->>G: schedule local notification (rule-based)
  C-->>B: prefs saved (profiles.notification_prefs)
  B-->>A: toggle on - reminder fires at preferred time
  note over C,G: rule-based - no AI involved
